title: Raspberry Fool
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Organic, Western, Take-out, Bakery, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A small comfort food cafe run by an owner who focuses on using local and seasonal items. Makes bread and baked goods in-house. Staff knows about veganism. Vegan choices might include a breakfast plate, bahn-mi style toasted sandwich, cake and biscuits. Has soymilk, large range of teas.
